---
title: Vegan Chickpea Coconut Curry with Basmati Rice & Garlicky Pita Wedges
description: Curries are one of those meals that warms your heart and your belly, and tonight’s vegan version is no exception. Chickpeas, onion, and tomatoes get a super savory treatment in a curry sauce made creamy with coconut milk. Spoon all this deliciousness over fluffy basmati rice, sprinkle with fresh cilantro, and serve with garlicky pita wedges for soaking up the curry. It’s one soul-satisfying meal!
